 Available Colours

#------------------------------------

 *{magenta}Magenta
 *{dark_blue}Dark blue
 *{purple}Purple
 *{dark_green}Dark green
 *{grey1}Grey1
 *{medium_blue}Medium blue
 *{light_blue}Light blue
 *{brown}Brown
 *{orange}Orange
 *{grey2}Grey2
 *{pink}Pink
 *{green}Green
 *{yellow}Yellow
 *{aquamarine}Aquamarine
 *{white}White (and of course black)

#CONTENT: line
