#------------------------------------

 K2 Limitations

#------------------------------------

 + The box *{GREEN}colours* are determined by
   the initial *{MAGENTA}foreground* and
   *{DARK_BLUE}background* colours ...

   + so the title and content box
     outlines are the same *{GREY2}(as here)

 + Underlines are only allowed if the
   following line is _*{AQUAMARINE}empty*_ at that
   location.

 + Underlines are in the colour of
   the content foreground even if the
   underlined text is a _*{YELLOW}different_
   colour.
